 could be applied to the coordination of logistic and\nproduction processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2008 13:23:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Feb 2008 07:59:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
