 DF model reproduces the power-law\nbehaviour of phase space density Q=\\rho(r)/\\sigma^{3}(r).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2008 15:05:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 May 2008 13:22:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
